overview: Come and discover the world of boxing in Private Gold, Boxing Beauties where the feisty Hannah Vivienne, Baby Nicols, Lucy Heart and debutant Monica Brown will duke it out and show their true colours for a shot at the title. Prepare for things to get viscous and of course heated as these girls will not hesitate to go to any lengths to win. Whether it’s a threesome with their trainers, DP with their coaches or just a good old fashioned fucking these horny competitors will do whatever it takes to reach their goals and you will not want to miss a minute! So strap in for a wild ride and get ready to rumble in Private Gold, Boxing Beauties and find out who will win the ultimate Private championship title…
title: Boxing Beauties
